265
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:15,115
Well, thank you. Thank you, man.

266
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:17,840
Hey, thanks for coming down.
I really appreciate that.

267
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,594
You... You're depressing
the hell out of me.

268
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,591
It may be better
if you took off. Yeah?

269
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:24,113
You got it, Sam.

270
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:26,794
- I'll see you.
- All right. Bye-bye.

271
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,718
Here you go, Sam.

272
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:34,759
I want you to have that.
It's kind of a family heirloom.

273
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:37,676
