- A truss.

274
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,994
It came over with my grandfather
from the old country.

275
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:44,355
Actually, it came over
on my grandfather.

276
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:49,713
Oh, well, yeah, gee,
that's nice. Thank you.

277
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:52,599
