278
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:55,877
You're Sammy.
Sammy don't wear no truss. Geez!

279
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:57,678
Oh, that's funny. That's very funny.

280
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,831
Yeah, well, don't pop
your stitches laughing.

281
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:05,074
