well into their latter years.

320
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:09,393
Listen to this:

321
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:14,552
Leo Tolstoy, Albert Schweitzer,

322
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:19,589
Grandma Moses, Bertrand Russell,
Picasso, Goethe...

323
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:24,311
- Oh, now, he's my favourite.
- Yeah, mine too. Mine too. He...

324
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,551
