325
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:34,439
Well, I just thought I'd make the room
look a little more romantic.

326
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:36,955
You keep reading.
You go right ahead.

327
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:39,680
Oh, Sam, this is wonderful.

328
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:43,440
An old person wouldn't be doing this.

329
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:48,754
This is the act of a vital,
strong, young man.

330
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,353
