331
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:54,149
Who wants sex.
Who won't get it.

332
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:01,797
But this is a very positive sign.

333
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:04,155
Ah, hey, come on, you know.

334
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:08,438
This is a chance of a lifetime
to play doctor in a real hospital.

335
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:09,589
Now come on.

336
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:11,830
It's tempting, it's tempting,
but I think not.

337
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:15,436
I'm going to go now and let you rest.

338
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:18,034
Yeah. Hey, listen.

339
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:21,915
I don't want you to make
too big a deal out of this,

340
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,479
but thank you very much for coming.

341
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:26,234
Your visit helped a lot today.

342
00:20:28,080 --> 00:20:32,710
Well, if we can't reach out
in our moment of need, if we can't

343
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:36,555
span the gap that separates
each human. If we can't allow...

344
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:40,030
Sweetheart, sweetheart, that's what
I meant by making too big a deal.

345
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:45,154
- Okay. Goodbye, Sam.
- Bye-bye.

346
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,039
Hi.

347
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:55,149
- Howdy.
- Hi.

348
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,356
